# TypeScript / Next.js

- `apps/web` on **Next.js 16** + React 19. Node **22+** (prefer 24 LTS). Prefer `pnpm`.
- Call **only** `services/gateway-service` (`NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL`).
- Product display name: **ai-finance-manager**.
- TypeScript **5.9.x** (stay on 5.x until Next/ESLint adopt TS 7 broadly).
- Strict TS; SC by default; secrets server-side; confirm-before-save for AI drafts.
- Money as integer minor units at boundaries; a11y required.
